### 1. Get Keycloak token
POST http://localhost:8086/realms/smart-travel/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

client_id=smart-travel-client&username=demo-user&password=demo-pass&grant_type=password

> {%
    client.global.set("access_token", response.body.access_token);
%}


### 2. Gateway health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health


### 3. Get Paris seed recommendations through Gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations?destination=Paris&type=ATTRACTION
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

> {%
    if (response.body.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("recommendation_id", response.body[0].id);
    }
%}


### 4. Create trip through Gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "demo-user",
  "destination": "Paris",
  "startDate": "2027-07-10",
  "endDate": "2027-07-15",
  "budget": 800,
  "currency": "EUR"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("trip_id", response.body.id);
%}


### 5. Trip Service calls Recommendation Service through Feign
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 6. Save recommendation to trip
POST http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/{{recommendation_id}}/save
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tripId": {{trip_id}},
  "userId": "demo-user"
}


### 7. Get saved recommendations
GET http://localhost:8080/api/recommendations/saved?tripId={{trip_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}


### 8. Estimate trip cost through Trip Service
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trips/{{trip_id}}/estimated-cost
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}